Test case to verify that the configurable "logout redirect URI" works as intended.

* Fixture: SocialRest

This test case assumes a logged in user.

| comment       | *Test Case: logout_redirect_uri* | |

| comment       | Setup: Set the logout_redirect_uri | |
| set           | test_logout_uri | http://www.google.com |
| st-config     | set logout_redirect_uri %%test_logout_uri%% | Wrote updated config |

| comment       | Test Case: Logout, and make sure we got sent to the right URI |
| get           | /nlw/submit/logout | |
| code-is       | 302 | |
| header-like   | Location | %%test_logout_uri%% |

| comment       | Teardown: set the logout_redirect_uri back to default | |
| st-config     | set logout_redirect_uri /nlw/login.html | Wrote updated config |
